<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your RSOLV Success Report</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 200px;
    }
    h1, h2, h3 {
      color: #10b981;
    }
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 4px solid #10b981;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #10b981;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .stat-label {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .achievement-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .timeline {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      display: flex;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .timeline-marker {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }
    .timeline-content {
      flex-grow: 1;
    }
    .pricing-highlight {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta {
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .cta-secondary {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://rsolv.dev/images/rsolv_logo_transparent.png" alt="RSOLV Logo">
    </div>

    <h1>Your 2-Week RSOLV Success Report üéâ</h1>

    <p>Hi <%= @first_name %>,</p>

    <p>Congratulations! You've been using RSOLV for two weeks. Here's a snapshot of what we've accomplished together:</p>

    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Issues Fixed</div>
        <div class="stat-number">{Map.get(@usage_stats || %{}, :issues_fixed, 0)}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">PRs Created</div>
        <div class="stat-number">{Map.get(@usage_stats || %{}, :prs_created, 0)}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Time Saved</div>
        <div class="stat-number">{Map.get(@usage_stats || %{}, :time_saved, "0 hrs")}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Security Issues Found</div>
        <div class="stat-number">{Map.get(@usage_stats || %{}, :security_fixes, 0)}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    :if={Map.get(@usage_stats || %{}, :issues_fixed, 0) >= 5}
    <div class="achievement-banner">
      <h2 style="color: white; margin: 0;">üèÜ Power User Achievement Unlocked!</h2>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">You've automated 5+ fixes. You're officially an RSOLV pro!</p>
    </div>


    <h2>Your RSOLV Journey So Far</h2>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">‚úì</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <strong>Week 1: Getting Started</strong><br>
          You set up RSOLV and started automating your first issues
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">‚úì</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <strong>Week 2: Building Momentum</strong><br>
          You've seen how RSOLV handles security, performance, and bug fixes
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">‚Üí</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <strong>Next: Scale Your Automation</strong><br>
          Ready to tackle your entire backlog? Let's do this!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-highlight">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">üéÅ Your Trial Status</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;">
        <strong>{10 - Map.get(@usage_stats || %{}, :fixes_deployed, 0)} free fixes remaining</strong>
      </p>
      <p>After that, it's just $15 per deployed fix. No subscriptions, no seat licenses!</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What's Next?</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Expand to more repositories:</strong> RSOLV works across your entire organization</li>
      <li><strong>Automate security audits:</strong> Tag all security issues for immediate fixes</li>
      <li><strong>Clean up tech debt:</strong> Let RSOLV modernize your codebase</li>
      <li><strong>Train your team:</strong> Share RSOLV with colleagues to multiply impact</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="https://rsolv.dev/dashboard" class="cta">View Your Dashboard</a>
      <br>
      <a href="https://rsolv.dev/pricing" class="cta-secondary">Explore Team Plans</a>
    </div>

    <h2>Need Help Scaling Up?</h2>

    <p>I'd love to help you get even more value from RSOLV. Here are a few ways we can help:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Schedule a 15-minute optimization call</li>
      <li>Get best practices for your specific tech stack</li>
      <li>Learn about volume discounts for teams</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Just reply to this email and let me know how I can help!</p>

    <p>Thanks for being part of the RSOLV community. Here's to many more automated fixes!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Dylan Fitzgerald<br>Founder, RSOLV</p>

    <p style="font-style: italic; color: #6b7280;">P.S. If RSOLV has been valuable to your team, I'd be grateful if you could share a quick testimonial. It helps other teams discover how automated fixes can transform their workflow!</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @email %>. If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can <a href={@unsubscribe_url}>unsubscribe</a>.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2025 RSOLV - Fix Security Issues Automatically. Pay Only for Fixes You Deploy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>